title: Celebrity Big Brother will say goodbye to TWO stars tonight - and housemates will decide who goes
text:

Celebrity Big Brother fans will say goodbye to two housemates tonight. 
However, Emma Willis revealed there's a cruel twist in store when it comes to the second elimination. 
While the public will determine one eviction, the housemates will decide the next - and they have no idea this is going to happen. 
"The gates of hell are being swung open for our celebrities. No more Mr Nice Guy," Emma explained. Celebrity Big Brother fans will say goodbye to two housemates tonight (Photo: Channel 5) 
"The housemates are expecting an eviction tonight but what they don’t know is there’s going to be a second shock eviction when the housemates will be forced to turn on each other and cull the dullest celebrity." Read More Celebrity Big Brother romance? Jamie O'Hara and Bianca Gascoigne get closer in the bedroom after he admits she's 'sexy' Emma dropped the bombshell during tonight's live show (Photo: Channel 5) 
US singer Stacy Francis, actor James Cosmo, American model Austin Armacost , reality stars Heidi and Spencer Pratt and Calum Best's mum Angie Best are all currently up for eviction. The housemates will determine the second eviction (Photo: Channel 5) 
But it looks like any of the remaining housemates could get the boot in the second elimination. 
As if the commotion won't be enough to stir up drama in the house, three new celebs will be joining the current line-up tonight.
